data.description: This home hits the Tri-Level Trifecta! The spacious living room rolls into the perfectly laid-out kitchen/dining areas. Main Floor laundry and half bath. Upstairs you will find 3 nicely appointed bedrooms and a large full bath w/double sinks & storage. The lower level has a 4th bedroom, full bath, and rec area. The basement level has additional washer and dryer hookups, ample storage, and extra space for your needs. The backyard features a fenced-in yard, which doesn't stop at the fence-line, lots of yard space behind the fence, (take a strool and look for the stakes.)a large deck, wooden playset, mature trees, and an area for grilling. Oversized 2 car garage enough room for a boat, camper, or 4-wheeler.
